Amazon’s Kindle Fire Seen Ranking No. 2 in Media-Tablet Market

-- B y   D a n i e l l e   K u c e r a
-- 
2011-12-02T17:01:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-02/amazon-s-kindle-fire-seen-ranking-no-2-in-media-tablet-market.html
Amazon.com Inc. (AMZN)  is likely to have
about 14 percent of the global media-tablet market in the fourth
quarter, ranking second to  Apple Inc. (AAPL) ’s iPad, IHS said.  Amazon will probably ship 3.9 million units of the recently
introduced Kindle Fire in the final three months of the year,
according to IHS researchers. Apple probably shipped 18.6
million units of the iPad in the period, IHS said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Danielle Kucera in San Francisco at 
